reviews.text: affordable, great food, good service.

A very good Japanese Grill Restaurant located inside Windsor Building at Causeway.

Very easy to find at right after the escalator. 

You need to get a waiting list at the touch screen computer. 

You can also choose cooked food if you prefer not to grill. But i still suggest you to cook your own. It’s fan and you do it the way you like it.

Please the mushrooms and the oyster they are very very good.
Nice lunch and decent price . Around 300 for 2 person. Cheaper during week day

reviews.text:
I tried the lunch set B with 100min and 150% meat. It cost $150 after service fee.

It's semi-buffet. It only provided one set of meat, but you can get as many stuff as you want outside the salad and dessert bar.
The bar has over 40 kinds of foods, drinks and desserts that feed me very full.

(Honestly, i suggest choose the normal 60min set . Even if only the salad and dessert bar is enough.
Reasonable price for all you can eat, nice place for group gathering.

Came here for late dinner after work. Waited for almost 1 hr. I didn't know can use the app to get the waiting ticket.... we ate the Lv3 buffet the beef quality was really good. There are other self served items like soups, salad, veggies, rice, drinks and dessert. We ate a lot. Sure will be back again.
Good price yummy food
Nice place for party with friends . But a little bit expensive

I tried the lunch set B with 100min and 150% meat. It cost $150 after service fee.

It's semi-buffet. It only provided one set of meat, but you can get as many stuff as you want outside the salad and dessert bar.
The bar has over 40 kinds of foods, drinks and desserts that feed me very full.

(Honestly, i suggest choose the normal 60min set . Even if only the salad and dessert bar is enough.

久聞牛角大名，但一直被佢地難 book 位嘅傳聞而一直未試。直至最近朋友約晚飯，決定嚟呢度，星期五晚幾經辛苦之下至攞到位，但仍然要等多30分鐘至有得入座。呢度地方很大很寛敞，卡位坐得非常舒適。限時100分鐘嘅放題有好幾個選擇，我地揀咗 Lv 3 嘅美國極上和牛放題，有好多款高質素嘅牛肉揀，仲有鷄、豬同各類海鮮。除此之外，呢度嘅自製牛角飯 (紫菜飯) 味道亦好好。雖然要限時食，但我地幾個人狂風掃落葉咁食完又叫，味覺同飽肚度完全滿足，只要有機會都會再返嚟幫襯。😋👍
太多人等位，但也不算抵食，沙律吧質素一般，地下黐立立。

Very modern shopping plaza with some nice restaurants
generally ok but somehow crowdy n many GC tourists
A local mall in Mong kok, very crowded all the time, not easy to get a table during dinner time. There aren't something very spectacular that attracts customers

Sushi quality is good in general.  most of the sushi feature with a longer piece of sashimi. Fish quality is geat  The Red Roll is my favorite.  The miso soap is nice too with good quality of seaweed and quite different from what I use to have in different stores.  The reason for a 3- star is that it is a bit overpriced though.  Almost HK$300 per head is a bit too much.
